WEBVTT

00:20.680 --> 00:22.210
It’s impossible.

00:49.850 --> 00:51.290
It's been forever.

00:55.610 --> 00:57.410
Were you...

00:59.400 --> 01:01.540
Were you alive?

01:03.500 --> 01:08.110
I pull off such difficult tasks all the time.

01:20.150 --> 01:21.420
You're alive.

01:24.550 --> 01:25.610
You're alive.

01:28.250 --> 01:29.460
I'm sorry.

01:32.800 --> 01:33.860
I'm so sorry.

01:51.900 --> 01:52.830
Jerk!

01:53.920 --> 01:55.370
You are alive, you jerk!

01:56.720 --> 01:57.750
You jerk!

02:07.880 --> 02:09.460
I missed you.

02:09.460 --> 02:12.180
I never forgot you, even for a moment.

02:12.780 --> 02:14.410
I don't care.

02:15.520 --> 02:17.150
I'm going to live alone.

02:18.190 --> 02:19.820
I'm going to become a nun.

02:28.730 --> 02:30.310
I love you.

02:31.390 --> 02:33.200
I said I love you.

02:49.010 --> 02:50.630
This is weird.

02:50.630 --> 02:53.060
It won’t snow in Uruk.

02:57.910 --> 02:59.010
If what I heard

02:59.010 --> 03:00.490
during orientation is true,

03:00.490 --> 03:02.920
this is the first snow in 100 years.

03:14.730 --> 03:17.220
That day, Lieutenant Yoon said,

03:17.220 --> 03:20.829
"It's snowing for the first time in 100 years."

03:30.070 --> 03:31.530
And then...

03:33.700 --> 03:37.280
"He walked toward me in the snow."

04:28.740 --> 04:33.810
Sorry for the late reply.

04:39.940 --> 04:41.550
I'm not breaking up with you.

04:44.130 --> 04:49.150
I won't break up with you even if you kill me.

05:39.210 --> 05:40.490
I've been telling you this all along.

05:40.490 --> 05:42.510
If you can't protect yourself, you can't protect either

05:42.510 --> 05:44.820
your woman or your country.

05:45.909 --> 05:48.659
You have to remember only one thing.

05:48.659 --> 05:49.280
What's that?

05:49.280 --> 05:51.580
Never get hurt.

05:52.380 --> 05:53.460
Good.

05:54.560 --> 05:55.640
Take the tools and

05:55.640 --> 05:58.270
assemble on the drill ground in five.

05:58.980 --> 05:59.640
Now!

05:59.640 --> 06:00.710
On it!

06:35.850 --> 06:38.690
You can't cry in front of your men.

06:38.690 --> 06:40.000
It’s improper.

06:45.030 --> 06:46.340
What happened with your test?

06:47.730 --> 06:49.300
I passed.

06:50.520 --> 06:52.760
Now I'm a high school graduate.

07:40.730 --> 07:42.400
I won't die again.

07:44.500 --> 07:46.790
I'll never ever die

07:47.590 --> 07:49.409
even if in the face of death.

07:54.180 --> 07:55.820
I don't trust you.

08:00.560 --> 08:03.090
But please keep your promise.

08:03.670 --> 08:06.500
It snowed for the first time in 100 years.

08:06.500 --> 08:08.820
You came back alive.

08:10.620 --> 08:13.410
I've used up all my luck now.

08:14.870 --> 08:17.400
You're all I have.

08:18.970 --> 08:19.880
Yeah.

08:21.050 --> 08:22.870
By the way, why did you get here?

08:25.220 --> 08:26.500
What about Shi Jin?

08:26.860 --> 08:28.780
I heard that you were here

08:29.580 --> 08:31.110
when I reported to headquarters.

08:32.070 --> 08:34.730
After leaving the Combined Forces,

08:34.730 --> 08:36.200
I came here

08:36.929 --> 08:38.870
and Captain Yoo went to Albania.

08:38.870 --> 08:41.450
What happened to you two?

08:41.909 --> 08:45.340
We thought you and

08:45.340 --> 08:46.040
Shi Jin were blown up

08:46.040 --> 08:47.950
and they couldn't even find the bodies.

08:56.010 --> 08:58.270
The militia got there
just before the bombing.

08:59.960 --> 09:02.950
Before the bombing, we were taken to a shelter.

09:03.710 --> 09:06.350
We were locked up underground somewhere.

09:07.050 --> 09:12.900
We were there for between 150 and 155 days.

09:20.970 --> 09:23.610
Let's take care of these two and get out of here.

09:35.140 --> 09:38.060
I'll pay for this snack even in the other world.

09:38.060 --> 09:39.870
I repaid you

09:40.990 --> 09:42.610
what I owe you.

09:44.470 --> 09:46.100
Good luck!

09:46.100 --> 09:51.700
My friend from far away helped us escape.

09:53.430 --> 09:55.430
Done.

09:55.430 --> 09:57.710
I guess you read my mind.

09:58.320 --> 09:59.110
I was going to teach you a lesson

09:59.110 --> 10:00.550
when you came back.

10:00.550 --> 10:02.470
My girlfriend is a doctor.

10:06.350 --> 10:08.580
When she put me in bed,

10:10.090 --> 10:11.720
I got really excited.

10:13.880 --> 10:16.240
I missed your silly jokes.

10:18.770 --> 10:20.780
I'm glad you came back.

10:22.400 --> 10:23.560
Ouch! Needle! Needle!

10:24.030 --> 10:25.710
-Needle! Needle!
-I'm sorry.

10:27.790 --> 10:29.130
You don't have to be sorry.

10:29.130 --> 10:30.250
I'm sorry.

10:33.850 --> 10:36.190
What's the UN's radio code?

10:58.650 --> 10:59.530
I won't do it again.

11:05.480 --> 11:07.180
Wow. I want to believe you again.

11:10.950 --> 11:12.110
I've been wondering

11:13.410 --> 11:14.480
what are those?

11:16.030 --> 11:17.370
They're for you.

11:18.360 --> 11:19.780
Today's the anniversary of your death.

11:21.600 --> 11:24.160
I had to prepare for your one-year...

11:27.890 --> 11:29.430
Are you...

11:31.100 --> 11:32.360
No way!

11:32.360 --> 11:33.630
What do you mean?

11:33.990 --> 11:38.750
Hi, Beauty! Here is your knife.

11:39.350 --> 11:40.990
Can you see that person?

11:40.990 --> 11:43.510
Yeah. He's very handsome.Boyfriend?

11:43.510 --> 11:45.350
Thank god!

11:45.350 --> 11:46.840
I thought I was the only one who can see things.

11:46.840 --> 11:48.010
- Thank you.
- Good night.

11:48.010 --> 11:49.010
- Good night.

11:51.520 --> 11:54.260
Wow, did you just kill me again?

11:54.620 --> 11:56.060
Did you think I was a ghost?

11:56.060 --> 11:57.040
You are a doctor!

11:57.500 --> 11:58.730
You're supposed to be a logical person.

11:58.730 --> 12:00.540
You came back on the anniversary of your death.

12:00.540 --> 12:01.960
Eat some fruit.

12:01.960 --> 12:03.120
Whether you're a ghost or not,

12:03.120 --> 12:04.860
these are for you.

12:04.860 --> 12:06.170
Drink some wine as well.

12:06.170 --> 12:07.180
I couldn't bring rice wine.

12:07.180 --> 12:08.320
You prepared

12:08.320 --> 12:09.520
a lot on

12:10.190 --> 12:11.510
foreign soil.

12:14.840 --> 12:15.910
Excuse me.

12:20.520 --> 12:22.680
You wench! Why haven't you called?

12:22.680 --> 12:23.720
I was worried.

12:23.720 --> 12:25.280
Sorry, I was caught up with work.

12:25.280 --> 12:26.290
You were caught up?

12:26.290 --> 12:27.050
Mo Yeon!

12:27.050 --> 12:28.500
Dr. Kang!

12:28.680 --> 12:30.270
Geeze.

12:30.270 --> 12:32.310
Why a video call all of a sudden?

12:32.310 --> 12:34.030
Hey! I can't see your pretty face.

12:34.030 --> 12:35.550
Go somewhere brighter.

12:36.120 --> 12:36.900
Okay.

12:37.990 --> 12:39.130
Better?

12:44.660 --> 12:46.770
Am I the only one who sees him?

12:48.530 --> 12:51.500
I can see him as well.

12:52.610 --> 12:53.770
Are you okay?

12:54.150 --> 12:55.380
You don't see him?

12:56.050 --> 12:57.430
See whom?

12:57.980 --> 13:02.600
Isn't today the anniversary of Captain Yoo's death?

13:04.880 --> 13:08.770
She set the table for him.

13:09.220 --> 13:10.630
Right.

13:10.630 --> 13:12.110
He went there to eat the food.

13:18.520 --> 13:20.180
You're killing me for the third time.

13:20.810 --> 13:21.600
Do you think it's funny?

13:21.600 --> 13:22.630
You've come back to life

13:22.630 --> 13:24.620
and you didn't expect something like this?

13:25.220 --> 13:26.780
Don't you think they're cute?

13:28.470 --> 13:29.480
I think they know now.

13:32.210 --> 13:33.220
Mo Yeon,

13:33.880 --> 13:36.060
listen to me and do as I say.

13:37.900 --> 13:39.310
Don't ask me why.

13:39.310 --> 13:40.410
What is it?

13:40.410 --> 13:42.560
Tell him that you love him

13:43.150 --> 13:44.480
and that you missed him.

13:45.780 --> 13:47.700
Express what's in your heart.

13:49.010 --> 13:50.560
So that he won't stay with you.

13:51.580 --> 13:52.560
What?

13:53.270 --> 13:54.570
You won't believe me

13:56.270 --> 13:58.620
but Captain Yoo's there.

13:59.300 --> 14:02.810
Please send him to where he belongs.

14:04.890 --> 14:05.920
Geeze.

14:06.360 --> 14:07.670
You just got here and he's asking you to leave.

14:08.250 --> 14:10.280
Wow! That hurts my feelings.

14:10.280 --> 14:11.370
Wow!

14:12.130 --> 14:13.100
This is crazy!

14:14.280 --> 14:15.970
-What’s happening?
- Oh my god!

14:15.970 --> 14:17.230
Hello, everyone!

14:19.150 --> 14:21.720
As you see, Captain Yoo's alive.

14:22.180 --> 14:24.800
You can imagine how happy I am tonight.

14:24.800 --> 14:27.280
I'll explain everything when I get back.

14:27.280 --> 14:28.530
Please don't interrupt us anymore.

14:28.530 --> 14:29.500
I’ll hang up the phone.

14:29.500 --> 14:30.580
Bye.

14:32.480 --> 14:33.280
That was Captain Yoo, right?

14:33.280 --> 14:35.020
- Yes, it was.
- Yes, it was.

14:35.020 --> 14:35.890
He wasn't a ghost or anything, right?

14:35.890 --> 14:37.030
I saw him.

14:47.820 --> 14:48.780
Attention!

14:49.340 --> 14:50.780
Salute to Commander Yoon...

14:50.780 --> 14:52.500
Thank you.

14:53.190 --> 14:56.310
Thank you for coming back alive.

15:02.530 --> 15:03.910
Captain Yoo Shi Jin!

15:05.250 --> 15:06.680
Sergeant Seo Dae Young!

15:10.000 --> 15:11.010
You jerks!

15:13.100 --> 15:14.930
Do you know how much it hurts me

15:14.930 --> 15:16.500
when I heard you two were...

15:18.510 --> 15:19.550
While you were gone,

15:19.550 --> 15:21.660
I got promoted. So what?

15:22.460 --> 15:24.120
I'm now ahead of all my friends.

15:24.120 --> 15:25.250
Sir!

15:25.250 --> 15:27.380
I looked good in newspaper articles.

15:27.380 --> 15:28.990
But I don't care about those things.

15:28.990 --> 15:30.210
Sir! Sir!

15:30.620 --> 15:32.130
I'm glad that you two come back...

15:43.730 --> 15:44.770
Yoo Shi Jin and Seo Dae Young's duty

15:44.770 --> 15:47.180
is writing a report about what happened.

15:47.180 --> 15:50.280
It should be as thick as the Bible.

15:50.960 --> 15:52.760
-Good to see you again.
-Each of you hard.

15:54.310 --> 15:55.280
Hey!

16:00.690 --> 16:01.660
What are you doing?

16:01.660 --> 16:05.150
I'm more scared of A4 than C4.

16:06.580 --> 16:08.580
Look at this sharp edge.

16:08.580 --> 16:11.470
It can cut you and it really hurts.

16:14.080 --> 16:16.890
One of the jerks who was torturing us with water

16:16.890 --> 16:18.710
had a Spetsnaz tattoo on his wrist, right?

16:18.710 --> 16:20.380
No, he's the one who cut us with a dagger.

16:21.710 --> 16:24.520
Let's not write about being beaten up all the time.

16:24.520 --> 16:26.490
Let's say we fought back once a week

16:26.490 --> 16:28.570
and tried to escape once a month.

16:28.850 --> 16:30.120
Let's write it as truthfully as we can.

16:30.120 --> 16:32.040
I wrote we escaped twice a month.

16:33.530 --> 16:36.660
They're not going to cross-check

16:37.070 --> 16:38.230
our report with the militia, right?

16:38.230 --> 16:39.940
They're going to believe whatever we say.

16:39.940 --> 16:41.200
We have to

16:41.200 --> 16:44.620
mix realistic and dramatic elements well.

16:45.920 --> 16:47.900
How about "Rambo" for reference?

16:49.810 --> 16:51.150
It's set in the Vietnamese War

16:51.150 --> 16:52.830
so the weapons and details won't match.

16:52.830 --> 16:55.110
Why don't we go with the Bourne series?

16:55.110 --> 16:57.180
Lieutenant Yoon likes Matt Damon.

16:57.180 --> 16:59.050
Okay. That's perfect.

16:59.380 --> 17:00.420
If you'll excuse me.

17:00.460 --> 17:01.410
Where do you think you're going?

17:02.520 --> 17:03.250
We need to write it consistently.

17:03.250 --> 17:04.420
We should write it separately.

17:04.420 --> 17:06.630
If I say one thing and you say another,

17:06.630 --> 17:08.220
the details won’t match.

17:08.220 --> 17:10.040
Why do I have to write the report?

17:10.040 --> 17:12.190
Lieutenant Yoon is in Uruk.

17:12.650 --> 17:14.510
Your girlfriend is away

17:15.319 --> 17:16.349
and you've got time.

17:22.700 --> 17:24.190
Do you remember that

17:24.190 --> 17:25.380
you dumped me here?

17:26.099 --> 17:27.200
I do.

17:28.610 --> 17:30.340
I might dump you again today.

17:30.340 --> 17:31.710
You must be joking.

17:32.370 --> 17:33.780
I suffer from trauma.

17:33.780 --> 17:34.850
I'm serious.

17:38.100 --> 17:39.810
I have a question for you.

17:41.020 --> 17:45.450
Are you planning to keep going back to the department store?

17:46.200 --> 17:48.440
I want to know if you want to become a hero.

17:51.670 --> 17:52.690
No soldier is interested

17:52.690 --> 17:55.960
in becoming a hero after death.

17:56.640 --> 17:57.680
All right.

17:59.140 --> 18:01.830
I go to the places where I have to keep peace.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.500
You want to keep doing it

18:03.500 --> 18:04.750
even if I'm against it.

18:04.750 --> 18:06.260
Are you against it?

18:06.260 --> 18:07.490
What do you want?

18:08.760 --> 18:12.850
What if you don't come back forever next time?

18:15.730 --> 18:16.910
Don't be scared.

18:17.510 --> 18:19.410
I'm not against it.

18:19.640 --> 18:21.550
What's the use of trying to stop you?

18:21.550 --> 18:24.870
You'll feel guilty, but you'll never give up.

18:25.740 --> 18:27.100
I'll hate you for that

18:27.100 --> 18:28.660
but I'll cheer for you in the end.

18:29.250 --> 18:30.350
I'd rather support you

18:30.350 --> 18:32.040
for keeping peace.

18:33.080 --> 18:34.570
As long as my support

18:34.570 --> 18:36.520
can give you peace.

18:39.080 --> 18:40.150
Thank you

18:40.700 --> 18:41.960
and I'm sorry.

18:42.460 --> 18:44.790
I'm sorry that the only thing

18:45.290 --> 18:46.380
I can say is "I'm sorry."

18:47.690 --> 18:49.060
I'm not dumping you.

18:49.060 --> 18:50.660
Do you want to go fishing tomorrow?

18:51.750 --> 18:53.180
It's some sort of mind therapy.

18:54.540 --> 18:57.070
I'll be amazingly cute, so don't be shocked.

18:57.880 --> 18:59.350
I'll be extremely happy,

18:59.350 --> 19:00.490
so be mentally prepared.

19:01.960 --> 19:04.750
Be thankful that you have a girlfriend like me.

19:15.060 --> 19:17.600
The scenery is beautiful and I feel peaceful.

19:18.490 --> 19:20.750
I feel like my emotional wounds are being healed.

19:24.540 --> 19:26.960
Nothing's happened for the past two hours.

19:27.810 --> 19:29.640
We didn't even catch one fish.

19:32.910 --> 19:35.800
Is your method of trying to heal the old trauma

19:35.800 --> 19:37.900
by creating a new one?

19:37.900 --> 19:39.880
I can't stand it anymore.

19:48.850 --> 19:50.420
There's an arboretum nearby.

19:50.420 --> 19:51.930
I have a new prescription for you.

19:51.930 --> 19:53.430
Let's go for a walk while breathing in clean air.

19:54.600 --> 19:56.960
Do you know how many kilometers I walk a year ?

19:57.840 --> 20:00.690
There's a temple. How about Jeoneumsa Temple?

20:00.690 --> 20:03.570
Do you know how many months

20:03.570 --> 20:05.500
I was locked up by guys with short hair?

20:06.030 --> 20:07.240
What do you want to do then?

20:08.300 --> 20:09.440
Something cliché.

20:10.630 --> 20:12.720
It's cold and we can't catch any fish.

20:13.520 --> 20:14.560
Why don't we take a break?

20:14.560 --> 20:15.290
Something just like this.

20:15.290 --> 20:16.140
There's only

20:16.800 --> 20:18.620
one room available.

20:20.600 --> 20:21.650
Don't cross the line.

20:21.650 --> 20:24.200
Are we going to stay in the same room?

20:24.200 --> 20:24.960
Of course.

20:24.960 --> 20:26.820
You said you wouldn't share the same bed with me

20:26.820 --> 20:27.610
when we were in the hospital.

20:27.610 --> 20:28.690
That's not me.

20:29.250 --> 20:31.460
She was a year younger than me.

20:31.460 --> 20:32.870
She knew nothing.

20:32.870 --> 20:33.850
Right?

20:35.040 --> 20:37.420
I didn't like her anyway.

20:38.130 --> 20:38.980
Huh? It got a bite!

20:39.200 --> 20:40.320
We're not done talking.

20:41.640 --> 20:42.740
Is it the fish or me?

20:45.830 --> 20:47.950
How come a soldier can't gut a fish?

20:47.950 --> 20:49.580
You came back from the dead.

20:50.470 --> 20:51.870
I won't get hurt. I won't die,

20:51.870 --> 20:52.680
but...

20:55.000 --> 20:56.260
I can't gut a fish.

20:58.390 --> 20:59.830
I'll let it go this once.

21:01.230 --> 21:03.660
I'll gut the fish. Scalpel.

21:06.630 --> 21:08.330
How merciless and ruthless you are!

21:15.300 --> 21:16.180
This room is nice.

21:17.330 --> 21:19.000
The bed looks big and comfy.

21:19.610 --> 21:20.580
Fool.

21:20.980 --> 21:23.380
The smaller and narrower the bed is, the better.

21:23.380 --> 21:24.590
Who's that jerk?

21:26.420 --> 21:28.560
Which jerk told you stuff like that?

21:29.730 --> 21:31.260
A jerk called Yoo Shi Jin.

21:31.890 --> 21:32.890
I had to survive a year without that jerk.

21:32.890 --> 21:34.450
I have to put this back.

21:36.380 --> 21:38.240
I'll put it back there.

21:38.840 --> 21:40.620
I'll put it back

21:40.620 --> 21:43.360
and forget everything.

21:43.360 --> 21:45.060
I'll forget everything and let you go.

21:45.470 --> 21:47.430
I reserved air tickets and cancelled them.

21:47.430 --> 21:49.250
I reserved hotels and cancelled them.

21:49.250 --> 21:51.440
I applied for vacation time and cancelled it.

21:53.140 --> 21:54.330
That jerk is really bad.

21:56.960 --> 22:01.150
Do you think we can go back there?

22:01.150 --> 22:02.660
With whom?

22:02.660 --> 22:03.870
With you.

22:04.780 --> 22:05.860
I'm excited.

22:07.060 --> 22:08.210
When are we going there?

22:08.430 --> 22:10.080
I don't know. Just wait.

22:12.160 --> 22:14.870
I'm going to make you wait forever.

22:17.170 --> 22:19.010
If that's the punishment,

22:19.010 --> 22:20.100
I'd gladly take it.

22:21.990 --> 22:24.860
If I say "now" one of these days,

22:24.860 --> 22:26.580
come to me immediately with your passport.

22:31.560 --> 22:34.000
By the way, where is the line you drew?

22:34.550 --> 22:35.970
I have to know so I won't cross it.

22:35.970 --> 22:36.970
You don't know?

22:36.970 --> 22:39.560
Now we're touching each other. It's so cold.

22:39.560 --> 22:40.670
Fool.

22:41.230 --> 22:42.370
Where my eyes stop?

22:43.010 --> 22:44.500
Where your heart lies?

22:56.040 --> 22:57.190
Not now!

22:59.650 --> 23:01.630
You're not an easy girl.

23:18.220 --> 23:19.640
How's it going with your report?

23:20.630 --> 23:22.720
I'm feeling the pain of creative writing.

23:23.990 --> 23:25.710
Do you know how to use the word processing program?

23:25.750 --> 23:28.050
I wonder what you think of me.

23:28.050 --> 23:29.410
As a man.

23:30.740 --> 23:31.700
Aren't you busy?

23:32.240 --> 23:34.080
I'm glad to hear your voice though.

23:36.490 --> 23:39.150
Every morning I wake up, I ask Ki Bum

23:39.730 --> 23:41.590
if I just dream that I saw you.

23:42.990 --> 23:44.150
When I woke up this morning, Ki Bum came to me

23:44.150 --> 23:49.370
and told me that it wasn't a dream and you actually did come back.

23:49.940 --> 23:51.900
But still I want to make sure.

23:52.690 --> 23:54.950
I want to hear your voice to make sure.

23:55.370 --> 23:56.470
Call me anytime.

23:57.180 --> 23:58.670
Even when I'm asleep.

23:59.320 --> 24:01.070
But I can't answer your calls tomorrow.

24:01.070 --> 24:02.430
I'm guarding some VIPs.

24:02.740 --> 24:04.070
VIPs?

24:04.390 --> 24:05.700
Who?

24:10.360 --> 24:11.310
This is Big Boss.

24:11.750 --> 24:13.030
Have the VIPs arrived?

24:13.030 --> 24:14.510
This is Piccolo.

24:14.510 --> 24:16.790
I've just spotted the car,

24:16.790 --> 24:18.160
the VIPs are in.

24:19.040 --> 24:20.350
This is Snoopy.

24:20.350 --> 24:21.820
The entrance is clear.

24:21.820 --> 24:22.950
Copy that.

24:22.950 --> 24:24.290
Everyone, come to the venue.

24:24.290 --> 24:26.230
I'll personally guard the VIPs.

24:26.230 --> 24:27.210
This is Wild Wolf.

24:27.210 --> 24:29.230
Big Boss, stand by where you are.

24:29.230 --> 24:32.740
Snoopy and I are in charge of the close-range security of the VIPs.

24:32.740 --> 24:34.690
Snoopy! Open the door!

24:35.540 --> 24:36.590
Roger!

24:38.730 --> 24:40.250
Wow! You're very quick.

24:41.320 --> 24:42.790
You should start a fast delivery service

24:42.790 --> 24:44.660
Instead of being a soldier.

24:50.850 --> 24:52.090
Hello, guys.

24:52.090 --> 24:53.340
2 3

24:53.340 --> 24:54.300
Happiness.

24:54.300 --> 24:56.710
Happy to be here. We're Red Velvet.

24:56.710 --> 24:57.940
Attention!

24:57.940 --> 25:00.090
Salute the soldiers!

25:00.090 --> 25:01.750
Sir!

26:05.560 --> 26:08.300
We love you, Kang Seul Gi!

26:10.770 --> 26:11.860
Oh my!

26:12.880 --> 26:13.550
What is it?

26:13.550 --> 26:14.480
What is it?

26:16.420 --> 26:18.350
Dr. Kang, you have to see this.

26:19.360 --> 26:24.520
We love you, Kang Seul Gi! Forever!

26:24.520 --> 26:26.000
23rd.

26:26.000 --> 26:28.110
Wasn't Captain Yoo on an operation on the 23rd?

26:28.110 --> 26:29.710
This is an important operation.

26:29.710 --> 26:32.830
I know. He's keeping  peace.

26:33.290 --> 26:35.160
That's not Captain Yoo.

26:47.440 --> 26:48.410
Please wait.

26:49.550 --> 26:51.540
Excuse me.

26:51.540 --> 26:52.420
Yes.

26:52.420 --> 26:54.070
Can you do me a favor?

26:54.070 --> 26:55.100
It's not in the script.

26:55.100 --> 26:56.250
Go ahead.

26:56.990 --> 26:58.410
Can you ask me if I have a boyfriend

26:58.410 --> 27:01.330
during the show?

27:03.550 --> 27:05.180
Kang Mo Yeon's Body Check. Season Two.

27:05.180 --> 27:07.560
We've learned about hyperlipidemia today.

27:07.560 --> 27:08.470
Before we go,

27:08.470 --> 27:12.200
there's one question that many viewers have been asking us.

27:12.200 --> 27:14.500
You're still single.

27:14.500 --> 27:16.980
Do you have a boyfriend?

27:17.880 --> 27:20.280
This is quite sudden.

27:20.280 --> 27:22.130
To prevent hyperlipidemia,

27:22.130 --> 27:23.370
it'd be nice to

27:23.370 --> 27:24.110
have a boyfriend

27:24.110 --> 27:25.160
to exercise with you.

27:25.160 --> 27:27.640
But I don't have one. I'm too busy.

27:31.230 --> 27:32.310
I enjoyed your show.

27:34.840 --> 27:36.770
You have no boyfriend because you're too busy.

27:37.520 --> 27:38.970
What am I then?

27:40.600 --> 27:41.760
Right. You are my best friend.

27:41.760 --> 27:42.790
I'm your best friend.

27:42.790 --> 27:44.390
My boyfriend was acting like

27:44.390 --> 27:45.570
he doesn't have a girlfriend.

27:45.570 --> 27:47.380
I thought I should do the same.

27:47.380 --> 27:49.440
I saw you on TV.

27:49.440 --> 27:51.270
You seemed to like that girl group.

27:51.270 --> 27:53.350
Soldiers one and two.

27:55.880 --> 27:58.860
Wow. I didn't know that you could dance.

27:58.860 --> 27:59.820
I thought you were a dancer.

27:59.820 --> 28:00.970
It's not what you think.

28:00.970 --> 28:03.020
I think it's how they cut it.

28:04.510 --> 28:06.130
Right. How they cut it.

28:06.130 --> 28:07.240
Yes. That’s right.

28:07.650 --> 28:11.100
I cheered when Commander Park was on stage

28:11.830 --> 28:13.690
and when they edited...

28:15.020 --> 28:18.120
You were whistling crazily when you saw Commander Park.

28:18.950 --> 28:21.310
Does Commander Park have fair skin like milk?

28:21.310 --> 28:23.440
His skin's rather smooth and fair.

28:25.460 --> 28:27.110
I'll kill you.

28:27.420 --> 28:28.710
Do you love Red Velvet?

28:29.130 --> 28:30.140
Whatever you say,

28:30.680 --> 28:32.040
I won't give up on you.

28:32.040 --> 28:33.060
Don't be silly.

28:33.460 --> 28:34.730
You were crazy about them on TV.

28:35.210 --> 28:37.290
I'll be back in 157 days.

28:37.990 --> 28:39.280
For the next 157 days,

28:39.280 --> 28:42.000
I'm going to think about how I can kill you when I get back.

28:42.000 --> 28:43.100
Got it?

28:43.490 --> 28:45.240
This is crazy.

28:45.240 --> 28:47.280
What did I do that was so wrong?

28:49.450 --> 28:52.030
This is what most people say

28:52.030 --> 28:52.840
and make

28:52.840 --> 28:54.830
things worse.

28:54.830 --> 28:56.370
However,

28:56.370 --> 29:01.610
I'm going to do my best

29:01.610 --> 29:02.820
so that you could show me mercy.

29:03.130 --> 29:04.890
Go ahead and try to win my heart.

29:07.270 --> 29:08.780
It's all my fault.

29:08.950 --> 29:11.050
Red Velvet didn't do anything wrong.

29:11.050 --> 29:12.420
I'm going to kill you today.

29:13.780 --> 29:16.090
Wait! Wait!

29:16.090 --> 29:17.860
Besides, I'm not a captain anymore.

29:17.860 --> 29:19.070
If you're not a captain, what are you?

29:20.890 --> 29:22.130
Were you fired from the army?

29:22.130 --> 29:23.390
No.

29:24.520 --> 29:25.630
I'm being promoted

29:26.470 --> 29:27.500
to major.

29:28.000 --> 29:28.960
Really?

29:30.060 --> 29:31.550
Why are you so happy?

29:31.550 --> 29:33.110
Are you getting a raise as well?

29:33.110 --> 29:35.420
Yes, but why are you so happy?

29:37.410 --> 29:38.600
And what's with the eyes?

29:39.200 --> 29:41.030
I'm trying to win you over with my eyes.

29:42.860 --> 29:43.820
You're so materialistic!

29:44.970 --> 29:46.050
I'm reporting to you.

29:46.050 --> 29:48.780
Captain Yoo Shi Jin has been promoted from captain

29:48.780 --> 29:50.640
to major on March 25th, 2016.

29:50.640 --> 29:53.850
Therefore,

29:53.850 --> 29:55.150
I'm reporting to you.

29:55.700 --> 29:57.020
Sir!

29:57.590 --> 29:58.650
Okay.

30:07.270 --> 30:09.180
The man I'm attracted to

30:10.780 --> 30:12.940
is a soldier of Korea, the only divided country left in the world.

30:12.940 --> 30:16.330
He's a major in the Special Warfare Command

30:18.420 --> 30:22.010
and still believes that he should protect

30:22.010 --> 30:24.940
seniors, the beautiful, and children.

30:27.980 --> 30:29.240
I'm still a doctor

30:29.700 --> 30:31.570
who runs a TV show.

30:35.230 --> 30:37.870
And the star of Haesung Hospital.

30:40.850 --> 30:43.160
I don't have to tell you who I am, do I?

30:43.550 --> 30:44.900
No.

30:45.980 --> 30:48.010
For 157 days,

30:48.010 --> 30:51.380
I've been trying to come up with ways to kill Seo Dae Young.

30:52.010 --> 30:53.020
I thought of you the entire time

30:53.020 --> 30:54.430
I was there.

30:55.270 --> 30:57.040
As a result,

30:58.220 --> 31:00.280
I was dying to see you.

31:07.730 --> 31:09.330
However, I didn't die and came back alive.

31:09.830 --> 31:10.970
Aren't you proud of me?

31:11.880 --> 31:13.900
I'm glad that you're back safe and sound.

31:15.750 --> 31:16.650
Cheers.

31:22.660 --> 31:23.990
I'm going to visit Commander Yoon tomorrow

31:24.840 --> 31:26.190
while holding your hand.

31:29.620 --> 31:31.610
Right. We have to talk about that.

31:31.610 --> 31:32.520
We don't have to.

31:33.320 --> 31:34.570
I'm not retiring from the army

31:34.970 --> 31:36.860
unless you take them off.

31:38.830 --> 31:39.680
Really?

31:39.680 --> 31:41.390
I'm going to tell your father

31:42.110 --> 31:43.540
while holding your hand.

31:45.720 --> 31:46.860
Let's go in the morning.

31:46.860 --> 31:48.220
The sooner, the better.

31:49.020 --> 31:50.600
I have a plan.

31:51.780 --> 31:52.990
You're going to go there drunk?

31:54.660 --> 31:56.840
I haven't had alcohol for two whole seasons.

31:58.370 --> 32:02.140
Go ahead and drink.

32:12.940 --> 32:14.630
I came here to drink

32:14.630 --> 32:15.660
the coffee you promised me.

32:17.340 --> 32:20.220
Sure. Have a seat. You too.

32:22.980 --> 32:24.460
Two coffees.

32:24.460 --> 32:25.450
Dad, I'm pregnant.

32:31.690 --> 32:34.420
No, sir. It's not true, sir.

32:34.920 --> 32:36.120
Is this the plan you talked about?

32:36.120 --> 32:38.720
You usually do stuff first and then confess.

32:38.720 --> 32:40.410
But I'm confessing first before doing it.

32:40.410 --> 32:42.880
When you're weak, a preemptive attack is the way to go.

32:44.710 --> 32:46.460
Does she have to be here?

32:47.920 --> 32:48.960
Go ahead and tell me.

32:49.290 --> 32:50.770
Whether it's a preemptive attack

32:50.770 --> 32:52.880
or carpet bombing, I don't care.

32:55.590 --> 32:57.730
But you don't say anything.

32:58.140 --> 32:59.470
I won't beat around the bush.

32:59.470 --> 33:02.920
I promised you that I'd retire from the army

33:03.440 --> 33:04.680
but I can't keep that promise.

33:06.790 --> 33:08.000
You can't?

33:09.510 --> 33:12.010
I was being tortured in the basement

33:12.010 --> 33:15.080
in someplace I didn't know,

33:15.710 --> 33:18.060
but I didn't regret being a soldier.

33:18.710 --> 33:22.530
I don't think my country should lose a soldier like me.

33:23.870 --> 33:25.150
I want to retire with honor

33:25.150 --> 33:26.690
when I feel it's time.

33:27.520 --> 33:31.060
I'll find another way to make you approve of me.

33:32.170 --> 33:35.820
This isn't about whether I approve of you or not.

33:40.240 --> 33:44.050
Your country already approves of

33:44.890 --> 33:45.900
Sergeant Seo Dae Young

33:45.900 --> 33:50.260
and as your superior

33:50.260 --> 33:51.470
I'm honored to have you as my son-in-law.

33:53.050 --> 33:55.070
Dad.

33:55.630 --> 33:57.220
When I sent you away, I've already approved of you

33:57.750 --> 34:01.550
and I deeply regretted the way I treated you.

34:02.170 --> 34:05.450
Right now,

34:05.950 --> 34:08.350
I'm so glad about your decision.

34:09.100 --> 34:10.030
Thank you.

34:12.300 --> 34:13.630
Dad.

34:19.060 --> 34:21.460
Take good care of my little girl.

34:23.980 --> 34:25.340
Yes, sir.

34:33.350 --> 34:35.139
Sergeant Seo's guardian is

34:37.659 --> 34:38.699
Mo Yeon Solgirl?

34:39.800 --> 34:43.310
Why do we always have a man between us?

34:46.710 --> 34:47.790
How have you been?

34:48.989 --> 34:50.780
As you can see, I'm doing well.

34:51.400 --> 34:53.670
How's the war between you and Sergeant Seo?

34:54.080 --> 34:55.350
Still a truce?

34:55.350 --> 34:57.460
No. We ended the war.

34:57.460 --> 34:58.740
Dad gave us his permission.

34:58.740 --> 35:01.170
Really? Congratulations!

35:01.670 --> 35:03.220
As fellow soldiers, we should have a drink.

35:03.220 --> 35:04.800
Anytime.

35:04.800 --> 35:07.840
Anyway, I'm here on other business.

35:18.380 --> 35:19.540
Hello, Mo Yeon.

35:19.540 --> 35:20.780
It's me, Fatima.

35:20.780 --> 35:22.750
I learn Korean.

35:22.750 --> 35:26.400
I will become a doctor like you later.

35:26.400 --> 35:27.660
Merry Christmas!

35:27.660 --> 35:31.990
Merry Christmas to all of you!

35:31.990 --> 35:34.390
I miss you and love you.

35:38.050 --> 35:40.010
Money well spent.

35:43.510 --> 35:46.130
Hello. Let me use the computer.

35:46.590 --> 35:47.820
Sure.

35:51.250 --> 35:54.610
Ms. Ha, what's Dr. Song's password?

35:54.610 --> 35:56.040
"I Am Genius."

35:59.640 --> 36:00.700
Come on.

36:00.700 --> 36:03.840
Lieutenant Yoon brought this from Uruk.

36:03.840 --> 36:05.070
Really?

36:05.070 --> 36:05.980
From Uruk?

36:14.200 --> 36:15.230
Wow! It's Blacky!

36:16.420 --> 36:17.520
Wow, he's gotten big.

36:18.840 --> 36:22.670
It'll be a while until those shoes fit him.

36:22.670 --> 36:25.510
His name is Blacky. And my name is...

36:30.360 --> 36:31.420
Huh? Blacky?

36:31.890 --> 36:33.530
Blacky! Blacky!

36:33.530 --> 36:35.560
His name is Blacky!

36:35.560 --> 36:37.970
And my name is...

36:39.500 --> 36:43.200
Baa... what? I couldn't hear it.

36:43.200 --> 36:44.320
Hold on.

36:49.000 --> 36:50.960
And my name is...

36:53.710 --> 36:55.300
What? And my name is...

37:05.540 --> 37:06.510
Geeze!

37:08.520 --> 37:09.950
Baa... what?

37:13.220 --> 37:16.110
I'll never find out his name.

37:17.250 --> 37:20.130
You'll be Blacky to me forever.

37:20.960 --> 37:23.320
Hold on. Don't turn it off.

37:24.170 --> 37:25.760
If I die here,

37:25.760 --> 37:27.460
go to the C drive of my laptop.

37:27.460 --> 37:31.100
Find a folder called "Bulbul" under "hospital."

37:31.100 --> 37:33.610
I want you to delete that folder.

37:34.140 --> 37:34.960
What's in there?

37:34.960 --> 37:37.220
You'll see more than you can imagine.

37:42.260 --> 37:48.100
My computer... my computer C drive.

37:50.240 --> 37:52.840
Right. Bulbul.

37:59.020 --> 38:01.150
If it's really from teens to thirties,

38:03.160 --> 38:08.310
I'm going to beat the crap out of him when I see him...

39:09.330 --> 39:11.060
I'm sorry. Are you okay?

39:11.060 --> 39:11.600
I'm okay.

39:11.600 --> 39:14.440
Let me do it. I'm her guardian.

39:14.440 --> 39:15.230
Sorry.

39:17.970 --> 39:21.370
Guardian?

39:21.370 --> 39:22.360
Forget it. I'm a little tired.

39:27.770 --> 39:28.950
If you're tired, sit down and get some rest.

39:29.320 --> 39:30.610
Don't let just anybody hold you.

39:33.670 --> 39:35.420
If you see something, tell me the truth.

39:35.810 --> 39:37.430
You've seen it. "1030."

39:37.860 --> 39:39.100
It was in the trash can.

39:39.100 --> 39:40.040
You told me to delete it.

39:40.040 --> 39:41.920
After I died.

39:41.920 --> 39:43.090
Why did you delete it?

39:43.090 --> 39:44.420
Why are you keeping them?

39:44.420 --> 39:45.910
To propose to you.

39:46.810 --> 39:48.340
It's my way of proposing to you.

39:48.340 --> 39:49.900
From my teens until my thirties,

39:49.900 --> 39:51.480
you're the only one.

39:52.210 --> 39:53.790
Don't you get it?

39:53.790 --> 39:56.920
How can you be sure it's not sympathy?

39:56.920 --> 39:58.900
What do you know?I know how I feel about you.

39:58.900 --> 40:01.680
This is love without a doubt.

40:02.870 --> 40:03.590
Please don't.

40:03.590 --> 40:04.550
Don't what? Confess?

40:04.550 --> 40:05.370
Whatever it is.

40:05.370 --> 40:06.700
I'll do it.

40:06.700 --> 40:08.450
Do what? Confess?

40:08.600 --> 40:10.870
Yes.After I pay off all my debt.

40:10.870 --> 40:11.780
Okay.

40:13.200 --> 40:14.110
What? Do you mean that?

40:14.860 --> 40:15.820
We're not done talking. Where are you going?

40:15.820 --> 40:16.790
To make money.

40:17.430 --> 40:19.840
Make money fast. Can't you get an advance?

40:19.840 --> 40:21.300
Can Dr. Kang lend you money?

40:37.010 --> 40:39.380
I don't know why I'm driving this car.

40:39.380 --> 40:40.510
Keep going straight.

40:40.510 --> 40:41.890
Go, Big Boss!

40:42.090 --> 40:43.400
I'm going.

40:43.400 --> 40:46.240
No. Not you. It’s this.

40:46.240 --> 40:47.920
This is Big Boss.

40:47.920 --> 40:49.200
Geeze.

40:50.040 --> 40:52.420
Do you love me that much?

40:53.110 --> 40:54.710
Did you have to name
your car my call sign?

40:54.710 --> 40:55.250
Yes!

40:55.250 --> 40:56.160
Geeze!

40:57.820 --> 41:00.910
Turn right, right there. Let's wash Big Boss.

41:01.730 --> 41:03.410
Not this Big Boss.

41:05.080 --> 41:06.560
Your timing is weird.

41:07.060 --> 41:09.460
I don't know why I keep driving this.

41:09.460 --> 41:12.970
Just do it.I don't want to ruin this car.

41:12.970 --> 41:15.710
I won't ruin my Big Boss.

41:16.630 --> 41:18.330
Your timing is weird.

41:35.170 --> 41:36.710
I might break up with her.

41:38.060 --> 41:39.110
It's too cold.

41:39.790 --> 41:40.730
What?

41:41.080 --> 41:42.110
I love you.

41:43.150 --> 41:44.300
Roll up the window.

41:44.300 --> 41:45.040
It's cold outside.

41:48.770 --> 41:50.650
You're making me get out of the car.

41:51.120 --> 41:52.230
It's cold outside. Hold this.

41:53.560 --> 41:55.190
Hold this.

41:57.820 --> 41:59.020
If I push this here...

42:02.550 --> 42:03.320
Water comes out.

42:03.630 --> 42:04.960
You're dead on.

42:05.310 --> 42:06.710
I'm sorry. I feel terrible.

42:07.460 --> 42:09.480
Now I've ruined your clothes.

42:13.310 --> 42:14.350
Put this on instead.

42:15.320 --> 42:16.470
I can see through it.

42:16.920 --> 42:18.680
I don't want other girls to see you.

42:20.070 --> 42:21.060
I can't break up with you.

42:21.710 --> 42:22.700
You're so sexy.

42:23.190 --> 42:23.870
Am I?

42:23.870 --> 42:26.160
You're sexiest when you smile.

42:27.750 --> 42:29.130
Please.

42:29.470 --> 42:30.430
I'm so cold.

42:30.970 --> 42:31.900
Hold me.

42:34.760 --> 42:36.280
Good girl.

42:47.180 --> 42:48.430
This is torture.

42:49.820 --> 42:51.200
Ahead and report me.

42:56.500 --> 42:58.220
Please let me eat lunch.

42:58.220 --> 42:59.230
I'm going to get sick.

42:59.230 --> 43:00.700
If you get sick, come to the dispensary.

43:00.700 --> 43:02.780
I'm only five minutes away.

43:03.700 --> 43:07.360
-That's so true. -Get sick.

43:10.640 --> 43:13.390
No. Should I break a bone or something?

43:16.510 --> 43:19.890
No. He can't go to Canada with a broken bone.

43:23.800 --> 43:25.270
Daniel and Ye Hwa are getting married.

43:26.380 --> 43:28.210
Daniel? That doctor?

43:31.130 --> 43:33.770
And they're getting married in Vancouver, Canada.

43:34.680 --> 43:35.750
We're invited as well.

43:36.380 --> 43:37.530
Wedding?

43:37.920 --> 43:40.190
Ye Hwa and Doctor Daniel?

43:40.190 --> 43:42.720
They're paying for our hotel and airfare.

43:43.770 --> 43:44.730
Wow!

43:44.970 --> 43:46.780
That's strange.

43:46.780 --> 43:48.660
Aren't they already married?

43:48.660 --> 43:49.670
No.

43:49.670 --> 43:51.640
They said they worked together.

43:51.640 --> 43:54.070
They told me that they co-owned the hardware store.

43:54.570 --> 43:59.440
Really? Yehwa's father is a Kareiski herbal doctor.

43:59.440 --> 44:01.500
He treated the rebels

44:01.500 --> 44:03.860
who were against the Russian government.

44:04.340 --> 44:07.930
Her father, mother, and brother were shot to death.

44:07.930 --> 44:08.950
Shot?

44:10.260 --> 44:12.390
Daniel managed to save Ye Hwa's life

44:12.390 --> 44:14.220
and went to the Canadian Embassy.

44:14.220 --> 44:15.530
They would only accept Daniel

44:15.530 --> 44:17.450
not Ye Hwa, a Russian citizen.

44:17.810 --> 44:18.630
Under international law,

44:18.630 --> 44:20.180
Refugee applications made in birthplace

44:20.180 --> 44:21.700
can’t be accepted.

44:22.070 --> 44:23.660
That's true. So?

44:23.660 --> 44:25.000
Daniel suggested that

44:25.390 --> 44:27.270
they get married right away.

44:27.270 --> 44:28.540
He asked for the forms.

44:28.870 --> 44:30.870
"She's my wife now, so protect her as well."

44:33.570 --> 44:34.650
That's how he saved Ye Hwa.

44:35.210 --> 44:36.600
Did you two talk about that as well?

44:37.170 --> 44:39.060
I told her about your will that I received

44:39.060 --> 44:40.600
and she told me that she lost her family.

44:42.770 --> 44:44.880
Did you read my will?

44:45.930 --> 44:47.520
Why would I read it?

44:47.920 --> 44:48.680
I know you just copied

44:48.680 --> 44:50.010
some cheesy song lyrics.

44:50.010 --> 44:50.890
I did not.

44:50.890 --> 44:51.900
Don't lie to me.

44:53.630 --> 44:55.540
"My plan was always to run away from you."

44:57.690 --> 44:59.400
"You, who's braver than anyone in the world,

44:59.980 --> 45:02.890
loves me, a pathetic loser like me."

45:03.860 --> 45:06.120
"Thank you and I'm sorry."

45:07.560 --> 45:11.940
"If you're reading this letter

45:11.940 --> 45:13.830
I'm hurting you

45:13.830 --> 45:16.250
until the last moment of my life."

45:17.290 --> 45:18.570
"Don't forgive me."

45:19.590 --> 45:22.590
"I hope you'll be as happy

45:22.590 --> 45:24.330
as much I cared for you."

45:24.330 --> 45:26.260
"I love you

45:28.450 --> 45:30.270
with all my heart, Yoon Myung Joo."

45:31.280 --> 45:32.920
"Whether I'm dead or alive,

45:33.870 --> 45:35.900
that won't change."

45:39.360 --> 45:40.610
Don't make it up

45:41.410 --> 45:42.800
You can't possibly have learned it by heart.

45:45.610 --> 45:46.830
Do you still carry it around?

46:00.120 --> 46:01.770
I wrote it more than 100 times.

46:03.610 --> 46:09.030
I wanted to run to you more than 100 times.

46:12.230 --> 46:14.020
Attention!

46:19.180 --> 46:22.070
Close your eyes if you rank lower than me.

46:47.430 --> 46:49.310
Close your eyes if you rank lower than me.

46:52.860 --> 46:54.270
Close your eyes.

47:20.380 --> 47:22.250
Whom are you going to give the money to?

47:23.000 --> 47:24.810
Most people will give it to Daniel,

47:24.810 --> 47:25.810
so Ye Hwa?

47:27.610 --> 47:29.170
You broke Daniel's car.

47:29.170 --> 47:31.470
I donate money to charity every month.

47:32.370 --> 47:35.170
You don't donate.

47:35.170 --> 47:36.580
You wouldn’t know how fulfilling it feels.

47:36.580 --> 47:39.810
Where's the girl who was looking for a briefcase full of money?

47:40.440 --> 47:41.800
She's getting more beer.

47:43.760 --> 47:46.010
I've been wondering.

47:46.010 --> 47:47.590
why were you the student representative

47:47.590 --> 47:49.380
on the picture?

47:50.170 --> 47:51.290
Because you were the top student?

47:51.290 --> 47:54.000
No, because I'm pretty.

47:56.210 --> 47:57.490
Not in alphabetical order?

47:58.330 --> 48:00.420
"Kang" always comes first in the Korean alphabet.

48:00.420 --> 48:01.280
No.

48:01.280 --> 48:02.530
I know. Seniors first?

48:05.020 --> 48:06.510
Didn't I tell you?

48:06.510 --> 48:09.320
I'm going to the school I graduated from tomorrow.

48:09.320 --> 48:11.440
I'm a graduate who honored the school.

48:11.900 --> 48:14.120
A graduate who honored the school.

48:14.120 --> 48:15.370
Were you the only student there?

48:16.940 --> 48:17.860
Aren't you going home?

48:18.190 --> 48:18.970
Traffic is bad at the moment.

48:18.970 --> 48:20.380
You said the same thing two hours ago.

48:20.380 --> 48:23.090
It's still bad.

48:23.090 --> 48:23.700
Especially around the Yeouido area.

48:23.700 --> 48:26.100
Hippocrates said the following.

48:26.100 --> 48:28.670
Actually, he said lots of things.

48:28.670 --> 48:33.900
I keep some in my brain and some in my heart.

48:33.900 --> 48:36.170
The following are some of them, for example.

48:36.170 --> 48:38.800
Now I'm allowed to work in the medical field.

48:38.800 --> 48:42.170
I'll carry out my duties with conscience and dignity.

48:42.170 --> 48:45.560
As a sergeant of the Republic of Korea Special Warfare Command,

48:45.560 --> 48:48.560
I will serve my country and people.

48:48.560 --> 48:51.140
Regardless of their race, religion, nationality,

48:51.140 --> 48:54.640
political party, or social status

48:54.640 --> 48:57.670
I'll carry out my duties to my patients.

48:57.670 --> 49:00.330
I will abide by the law and regulations

49:00.330 --> 49:03.600
and carry out my given duties sincerely.

49:03.600 --> 49:05.230
Even under threat,

49:05.230 --> 49:07.950
I will not use my knowledge inhumanely.

49:07.950 --> 49:10.450
Even under threat,

49:11.120 --> 49:14.420
I will not step back from any crisis.

49:15.600 --> 49:18.210
Even while facing a gun,

49:18.210 --> 49:20.380
I will keep the peace of the world.

49:23.530 --> 49:25.360
Today, many Yoo Shi Jins

49:26.020 --> 49:29.500
and many Kang Mo Yeons took their oaths solemnly

49:31.100 --> 49:32.610
I hope their oaths will be kept

49:33.560 --> 49:35.370
under any circumstances,

49:36.530 --> 49:41.100
and under the sun of this entire world.

49:41.100 --> 49:42.810
I really hope that.

49:55.510 --> 49:56.570
Now!

50:10.960 --> 50:13.370
We really came back.

50:14.980 --> 50:17.870
I'm glad that

50:18.700 --> 50:20.120
I came with you again.

50:20.120 --> 50:22.290
I missed my chance to come with another guy.

50:23.950 --> 50:25.080
Another guy?

50:25.080 --> 50:26.520
I can't come here alone

50:26.520 --> 50:27.770
with this pretty face.

50:27.770 --> 50:30.590
Guys won't let me.

50:32.330 --> 50:33.780
Stop right there.

50:33.780 --> 50:36.140
By the way, doesn't this ship look like an X-ray?

50:36.430 --> 50:37.800
Don't change the subject.

50:37.800 --> 50:39.160
Stop. Stay right there.

50:39.730 --> 50:40.730
Perfect.

50:44.060 --> 50:47.420
I only had your X-ray.

50:47.880 --> 50:50.520
I looked at it over and over again.

50:50.520 --> 50:52.350
I'm not going to let you off easy, whatever you do.

50:52.350 --> 50:55.110
Playing catch is fun at the beach.

50:55.110 --> 50:56.680
Catch me if you can.

50:57.600 --> 50:59.010
If I catch you, you're dead.

51:07.660 --> 51:09.280
When are we going back?

51:09.780 --> 51:12.490
When that boat turns into that ship.

51:13.500 --> 51:14.840
Really?

51:14.840 --> 51:18.880
I'm all alone with a guy on a deserted island.

51:20.150 --> 51:21.430
This is awesome!

51:49.370 --> 51:50.520
Aren't you going to have a sip?

51:51.080 --> 51:52.760
This is good.

51:53.510 --> 51:58.630
I really want to but I have to drive the boat.

51:58.630 --> 51:59.840
You said we weren't going.

52:00.700 --> 52:01.910
You'd like that, right?

52:10.610 --> 52:11.670
Is it yummy?

52:12.620 --> 52:13.420
Yes. I guess you really want to taste it.

52:14.990 --> 52:16.380
You know a way, right?

52:17.960 --> 52:19.120
There's a way.

52:21.800 --> 52:22.790
I know.

52:25.460 --> 52:28.040
I thought my heart would explode back then.

52:28.410 --> 52:30.600
My heart is going to explode now.

52:32.600 --> 52:37.210
We're at the beach and I have wine and a woman.

52:41.370 --> 52:43.440
The stars are shining in the sky.

52:47.380 --> 52:51.060
Oh my! Unbelievable!

52:52.570 --> 52:54.010
I've never seen a shooting star.

52:56.910 --> 52:58.610
What have you done?

52:59.970 --> 53:02.580
Why are all the stars here?

53:02.770 --> 53:04.020
Aren't you going to make a wish?

53:07.090 --> 53:08.340
I’ve already done.

53:08.340 --> 53:09.680
With your mouth open?

53:11.500 --> 53:12.710
Why don't you go up there

53:12.710 --> 53:15.700
and pick a star for me?

53:19.640 --> 53:20.800
I did.

53:21.760 --> 53:22.910
It's sitting beside me.

53:27.620 --> 53:28.620
Keep going.

53:32.210 --> 53:33.740
You're shining brightly.

53:35.390 --> 53:36.710
Keep going.

53:40.960 --> 53:45.330
My life has become brighter.

53:48.760 --> 53:50.220
You flatter me.

53:55.040 --> 53:56.310
How did I

53:57.580 --> 53:58.930
end up with a girl like you?

54:01.010 --> 54:03.020
I guess you saved our country.

54:04.860 --> 54:06.600
I think you were a constable in a previous life.

54:09.520 --> 54:11.410
I've been promoted in this life.

54:12.600 --> 54:14.650
Are we going to meet in our next lives as well?

54:14.650 --> 54:16.780
You're saving our country again.

54:18.210 --> 54:21.630
I have to at least save a country to be with you.

54:21.630 --> 54:22.900
Who said I'd be with you?

54:24.320 --> 54:25.800
Aren't we going to meet again in our next lives?

54:27.010 --> 54:27.740
If I say no,

54:27.740 --> 54:28.780
you won't come to see me?

54:30.300 --> 54:33.740
Please come to see me in our next lives.

54:34.540 --> 54:35.850
It's a promise.

54:43.230 --> 54:46.020
What was your wish?

54:47.080 --> 54:50.080
You'd be surprised.

54:50.080 --> 54:51.030
What is it?

54:53.860 --> 54:57.880
Let this man kiss me.

54:59.410 --> 55:00.560
Will it come true?

55:03.210 --> 55:06.070
There's a way.

55:41.590 --> 55:42.870
I love you.

55:47.120 --> 55:49.210
Me too.

55:50.870 --> 55:52.570
It was a question.

55:56.440 --> 55:59.150
I love you. That's my answer.

56:02.140 --> 56:03.490
Me too.

56:30.510 --> 56:32.390
By the way, don't you have to buy

56:32.390 --> 56:34.370
a wedding present

56:34.920 --> 56:36.670
instead of just giving money?

56:36.670 --> 56:38.590
Money is welcome everywhere in the world.

56:43.340 --> 56:45.760
It's easy to give and receive.

56:49.420 --> 56:50.250
Let's go.

56:56.930 --> 56:59.290
The bride and groom are getting changed.

57:00.430 --> 57:02.220
Ye Hwa looked so pretty

57:02.220 --> 57:03.360
in her wedding gown.

57:03.780 --> 57:05.340
Her wedding gown was so special.

57:05.340 --> 57:07.570
This scene here is special as well.

57:09.400 --> 57:12.520
Can't you do something with it?

57:12.880 --> 57:14.450
Why did you accept it?

57:14.450 --> 57:16.660
The bride threw it as hard as she could.

57:16.660 --> 57:17.660
I can't throw it away.

57:19.760 --> 57:20.850
Let him enjoy it.

57:21.060 --> 57:23.720
He got lots of stories about weddings.

57:24.480 --> 57:25.500
His ex.

57:29.480 --> 57:31.190
Don't you love endings like this?

57:31.730 --> 57:33.180
love endings like this?

57:33.180 --> 57:34.650
A"we-overcame-all-problems-with-love"

57:34.650 --> 57:36.880
"and-lived-happily-ever-after"

57:37.300 --> 57:38.830
ending.

57:42.000 --> 57:42.930
Time to kiss?

57:43.270 --> 57:44.670
Are they starting a show or something?

57:44.670 --> 57:46.000
The entire city of Vancouver?

57:46.000 --> 57:47.970
What a grand scale!

57:47.970 --> 57:49.640
This isn't a flashback.

57:49.640 --> 57:51.030
What's going on?

57:51.520 --> 57:52.480
This isn't

57:52.480 --> 57:54.740
a romantic comedy or a melodrama.

57:56.090 --> 57:59.180
It was a volcano! A volcano just erupted!

58:00.110 --> 58:02.480
Oh my!

58:03.590 --> 58:06.750
I knew this was too good to be true.

58:06.750 --> 58:08.690
I knew this was too good to be true.

58:08.690 --> 58:09.980
Too late.

58:11.680 --> 58:12.840
Get up.

58:12.840 --> 58:13.630
Okay.

58:15.450 --> 58:17.730
Are we going to start working again?

58:17.730 --> 58:19.910
I think it's time for me to destroy you.

58:19.910 --> 58:23.110
This is the beginning of a long report.

58:24.150 --> 58:25.580
Let's go.
